Odaily Planet Daily News 0G Foundation has announced the preliminary token economic model, with a total supply of 1 billion tokens and an initial circulation of 27.96% at TGE. The specific distribution plan is as follows: 
1) Community rewards: 9.69%, 2.4% unlocked at TGE; 
2) Ecological growth: 31.31%, 72.6% unlocked at TGE; 
3) Alignment nodes: 15%, 33.3% unlocked at TGE; 
4) Team, contributors, consultants: 22%, locked for 12 months, then gradually unlocked in the next 36 months; 5) Supporters (investors): 22%, locked for 12 months, then gradually unlocked in the next 36 months. 
0G Foundation added that the above is a preliminary overview, and the specific distribution ratio and lock-up time may change.
